OL,4,Chelicopter crash says MoD 'locked away
OL,5,Cfiles'
OL,7,FThe brother of a man who was killed in
OL,8,Fan RAF Chinook helicopter crash says
OL,9,Fthe Ministry of Defence (MoD) has
OL,10,Flocked away files relating to the
OL,11,Faccident for 100 years.
OL,13,F29 people were killed when the
OL,14,Fhelicopter carrying leading security
OL,15,Fpersonnel crashed on the Mull of
OL,16,FKintyre peninsula in Argyll and Bute
OL,17,Fon 2 June 1994.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/12
