OL,3,CBrother of man killed in RAF
OL,4,Chelicopter crash says MoD 'locked away
OL,5,Cfiles'
OL,7,FFlight lieutenants Richard Cook and
OL,8,FJonathan Tapper were initially accused
OL,9,Fof gross negligence over the crash.
OL,11,FHowever, a review of the incident in
OL,12,F2011 found the pilots should not have
OL,13,Fbeen blamed.
OL,15,FMr Cook said: "I find it extremely
OL,16,Fdisappointing that the families and
OL,17,Floved ones of the 29 passengers and
OL,18,Fcrew continue to be treated with such
OL,19,Fdisrespect by the MoD.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
