OL,3,CBrother of man killed in RAF
OL,4,Chelicopter crash says MoD 'locked away
OL,5,Cfiles'
OL,7,F"Irrespective of the controversy that
OL,8,Ffollowed this disaster and the
OL,9,Fsubsequent long campaign that both my
OL,10,Fand the Tapper family went through to
OL,11,Fget justice for the two deceased
OL,12,Fpilots, there is a continued
OL,13,Funacceptable lack of recognition or
OL,14,Frespect by the MoD of the service that
OL,15,Feach of these 29 brave individuals
OL,16,Fgave to their country."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/12
