OL,7,FThe independent review, announced in
OL,8,F2010 and published in 2011, found that
OL,9,Fcriticism of the Board of Inquiry on
OL,10,Fthe grounds that insufficient
OL,11,Fattention was paid to airworthiness
OL,12,Fand maintenance aspects was
OL,13,Funjustified.
OL,15,FA spokesperson from the MoD said: "The
OL,16,FMull of Kintyre was a tragic accident
OL,17,Fand our thoughts and sympathies remain
OL,18,Fwith the families, friends and
OL,19,Fcolleagues of all those who died.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/12
