OL,3,CBrother of man killed in RAF
OL,4,Chelicopter crash says MoD 'locked away
OL,5,Cfiles'
OL,7,F"In 2010 the Mull of Kintyre
OL,8,Findependent review was carried out and
OL,9,Fthe findings were fully accepted.
OL,11,F"The review did not find new evidence
OL,12,Fto suggest mechanical failure, and no
OL,13,Fsafety issues with the Chinook mark 2
OL,14,Fwere raised in the report."
OL,16,FChris Cook, a commercial pilot
OL,17,Fhimself, said: "I've never been into
OL,18,Fconspiracy theories to do with this,
OL,19,Fthere's a lot of them about.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/12
