OL,3,CBrother of man killed in RAF
OL,4,Chelicopter crash says MoD 'locked away
OL,5,Cfiles'
OL,7,F"I don't want to use hostile language
OL,8,Flike, there's been a blatant cover-up,
OL,9,Fbut when you hear things like this you
OL,10,Fwonder what other information is out
OL,11,Fthere that they're not letting us see.
OL,13,F"We have questions to why that is.
OL,14,FWhat's in there that would make them
OL,15,Fdo that?
OL,17,F"Or is it a case of they want the
OL,18,Fwhole thing shut down until we're long
OL,19,Fgone? And the next generation are
OL,20,Fprobably long gone."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/12
