OL,3,CBrother of man killed in RAF
OL,4,Chelicopter crash says MoD 'locked away
OL,5,Cfiles'
OL,7,F"It appears from the MoD's statement
OL,8,Fthat they still don't accept, after
OL,9,Fall this time and after all the
OL,10,Freports including the official Mull of
OL,11,FKintyre review, that there could have
OL,12,Fbeen any safety issues with the
OL,13,FChinook Mark 2 going into service,
OL,14,Fwhich I find staggering.
OL,16,F"Especially as it's been proven that
OL,17,FBoscombe Down had grounded it because
OL,18,Fthere were known safety issues with
OL,19,Fthe aircraft.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/12
