OL,3,CBrother of man killed in RAF
OL,4,Chelicopter crash says MoD 'locked away
OL,5,Cfiles'
OL,7,F"The fact that the MoD have had the
OL,8,Fofficial files on this crash locked
OL,9,Faway for 100 years, till 2094, does
OL,10,Fraise serious questions regarding a
OL,11,Fcover-up. Since this came to light,
OL,12,Fmany of the bereaved families are now
OL,13,Fvery concerned that a cover-up has
OL,14,Foccurred."
OL,16,FMr Cook and other families are now
OL,17,Fplanning to travel to the Mull of
OL,18,FKintyre on the anniversary of the
OL,19,Fcrash for a church-led remembrance
OL,20,Fservice.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/12
