OL,7,FThe service has been organised by the
OL,8,Flocal parish minister, Reverend Steven
OL,9,FSass, who has been liaising with an
OL,10,Farmy chaplain in Northern Ireland.
OL,12,FReverend Roddy McNidder, who was the
OL,13,Fparish minister at the time of the
OL,14,Fcrash in 1994, will deliver the sermon.
