OL,7,FRev Sass, Minister of Southend Parish
OL,8,FChurch, said: "We hope that as many of
OL,9,Fthe families as possible will join us.
OL,10,FWe want them to feel welcome and
OL,11,Fsupported, and we hope that this act
OL,12,Fof remembrance will give them the
OL,13,Fsupport which they need on this
OL,14,Fimportant anniversary.
OL,16,F"After the church service, which
OL,17,Fstarts at 12.30pm, we will travel to
OL,18,Fthe memorial cairn at the crash site
OL,19,Ffor a special act of remembrance at
OL,20,F3pm."
